Package eu.h2020.helios_social.extension.socialcommunitydetection

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveCENListener
    This class is used to make the CEN listener active.
    Community
    This class represents a community
    IdleCENListener
    This class is used to make the CEN listener idle.
    InternalMessage
    This class model a message used by the protocol
    SocialCommunityCENListener
    This class acts as a wrapper for the CEN listener, changing its behaviour according to the status of the module (idle when the module is not working, active when the module is working)
    SocialCommunityDetection
    This is the class used to manage the community detection module.
    SocialCommunityMessageReceiver
    Implementation of the HeliosMessagingReceiver for the Social Community Detection module.
    SocialCommunitySetupper
    Support class used to start the social community detection module.
